     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr-FR\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"fr-FR\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : EnsembleValeurs jdv-modalite-acquisition-cisis</b></p><a name=\"jdv-modalite-acquisition-cisis\"> </a><a name=\"hcjdv-modalite-acquisition-cisis\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">version : 9; Dernière mise à jour : 2026-04-20 16:58:26+0200; Langue : fr-FR</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profil: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/shareablevalueset.html\">Shareable ValueSet</a></p></div><ul><li>Include ce(s) code(s) tel qu'il(s) est (sont) défini(s) dans <a href=\"http://dicom.nema.org/resources/ontology/DCM\"><code>http://dicom.nema.org/resources/ontology/DCM</code></a><span title=\"La version est explicitement indiquée comme étant 01\"> version ?01</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Affichage</b></td><td><b>Définition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-AR\">AR</a></td><td>Autoréfraction</td><td>Autorefraction device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-BDUS\">BDUS</a></td><td>Échodensitométrie osseuse</td><td>Ultrasound Bone Densitometry (modality)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-BI\">BI</a></td><td>Imagerie biomagnétique</td><td>Biomagnetic imaging device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-BMD\">BMD</a></td><td>Ostéodensitométrie</td><td>Bone Mineral Densitometry by X-Ray (modality), including dual-energy X-Ray absorptiometry (DXA) and morphometric X-Ray absorptiometry (MXA)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-CR\">CR</a></td><td>Radiographie assistée par ordinateur</td><td>Computed Radiography device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-CT\">CT</a></td><td>Tomodensitométrie</td><td>Computed Tomography device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-DG\">DG</a></td><td>Diaphanographie</td><td>Diaphanography device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-DMS\">DMS</a></td><td>Dermoscopie</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-DX\">DX</a></td><td>Radiographie numérique</td><td>Digital Radiography device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-ECG\">ECG</a></td><td>Électrocardiographie</td><td>Electrocardiography device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-EEG\">EEG</a></td><td>Électroencéphalographie</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-EMG\">EMG</a></td><td>Électromyographie</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-EOG\">EOG</a></td><td>Électrooculographie</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-EPS\">EPS</a></td><td>Électrophysiologie cardiaque</td><td>Cardiac Electrophysiology device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-ES\">ES</a></td><td>Endoscopie</td><td>Endoscopy device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-GM\">GM</a></td><td>Microscopie générale</td><td>General Microscopy device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-HD\">HD</a></td><td>Onde hémodynamique</td><td>Hemodynamic Waveform acquisition device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-IO\">IO</a></td><td>Radiographie intrabuccale</td><td>Intra-oral Radiography device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-IVOCT\">IVOCT</a></td><td>Tomographie par cohérence optique intravasculaire</td><td>An acquisition device, process or method that performs intravascular optical coherence tomography</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-IVUS\">IVUS</a></td><td>Ultrasonore intravasculaire</td><td>Intravascular Ultrasound device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-KER\">KER</a></td><td>Kératométrie</td><td>Keratometry device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-LEN\">LEN</a></td><td>Lensométrie</td><td>Lensometry device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-LS\">LS</a></td><td>Scan laser</td><td>Laser surface scan device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-MG\">MG</a></td><td>Mammographie</td><td>Mammography device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-MR\">MR</a></td><td>Résonance magnétique</td><td>Magnetic Resonance device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-NM\">NM</a></td><td>Médecine nucléaire</td><td>Nuclear Medicine device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-OAM\">OAM</a></td><td>Mesures axiales ophtalmiques</td><td>Measurements of the axial length of the eye, which are done by various devices</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-OCT\">OCT</a></td><td>Tomographie à cohérence optique</td><td>Modality device that uses an interferometric, non-invasive optical tomographic technique to image 2D slices and 3D volumes of tissue using visible and near visible frequencies</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-OP\">OP</a></td><td>Photographique ophtalmique</td><td>Ophthalmic photography modality</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-OPM\">OPM</a></td><td>Cartographie ophtalmique</td><td>Modality device that measures corneal topography, corneal or retinal thickness, and other similar parameters that are typically displayed as maps</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-OPT\">OPT</a></td><td>Tomographie ophtalmique</td><td>Tomography of the eye acquired by a modality that is based on light and optical principles. Tomography based on other principles, such as ultrasound, is excluded</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-OPTBSV\">OPTBSV</a></td><td>Tomographie ophtalmique B-scan analyse de volume</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-OPTENF\">OPTENF</a></td><td>Tomographie ophtalmique en face</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-OPV\">OPV</a></td><td>Champ visuel ophtalmique</td><td>Modality device that measures visual fields and perform visual perimetry</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-OSS\">OSS</a></td><td>Scanner optique de surface</td><td>An acquisition device, process or method that performs optical surface scanning</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-POS\">POS</a></td><td>Détecteur de position</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-PT\">PT</a></td><td>TEP : Tomographie par émission de positons</td><td>Positron emission tomography (PET) device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-PX\">PX</a></td><td>Panaromique X-Ray</td><td>Panoramic X-Ray device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-RESP\">RESP</a></td><td>Onde respiratoire</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-RF\">RF</a></td><td>Radio-fluoroscopie</td><td>Radiofluoroscopy device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-RG\">RG</a></td><td>Imagerie radiographique</td><td>Radiographic imaging (conventional film/screen)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-RTIMAGE\">RTIMAGE</a></td><td>Image RT</td><td>Radiotherapy Imaging device; includes portal imaging</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-SM\">SM</a></td><td>Microscopie à lames</td><td>Slide Microscopy</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-SRF\">SRF</a></td><td>Réfraction subjective</td><td>Subjective Refraction device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-TG\">TG</a></td><td>Thermographie</td><td>Thermography device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-US\">US</a></td><td>Échographie</td><td>Ultrasound device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-VA\">VA</a></td><td>Acuité visuelle</td><td>Visual Acuity device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-XA\">XA</a></td><td>Angiographie X-Ray</td><td>X-Ray Angiography device</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/codesystem-dicom-dcim.html#dicom-dcim-XC\">XC</a></td><td>Caméra de photographie externe</td><td>External-camera Photography device</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
